<h3>Overview</h3>
<p>GrokPaste is a pastebin application which allows developers to exchange code snippets. 
	Grokpaste uses <a href="http://www.pygments.org">pygments</a> to provide syntax highlighting.
I have used <a href="http://dpaste.com">dpaste.com</a>'s layout and styling.	
</p>
<p>My intention of creating GrokPaste was to demonstrate the ease of developing with <a href="http://grok.zope.org">Grok</a>, as well as learn Grok/Zope3 technologies. </p>

